        Fortune
      
      , October 13, 2003; November 14, 2005; March 20, 2006; October 16, 2006.
    


        Harper's Bazaar
      
      , September 2001.
    


        Institutional Investor
      
      , August 2002.
    


        International Herald Tribune
      
      , June 3, 2003.
    


        Newsweek
      
      , December 27, 2004.
    


        Times
      
       (London, England), September 6, 2003; April 1, 2006.
    

      Xinhua News Agency, March 4, 2006.
    

