Andrea Jung
				










By CJ: Ravi Juneja | Views: 6112 | Comments: 
				
					0
				
			 
Send
			as a e-Card | Mail










Andrea Jung, the Chairwoman and CEO of Avon Products, is the sixth most powerful business women, according to the Fortune. Andrea Jung became the first female CEO in Avon's history in 1999 and Chairwoman in 2001. In her first five years as CEO, Avon's revenues rose from $5.3 billion to $7.7 billion and present sales have risen to nearly $11 billion. Andrea Jung is also the longest-serving woman CEO of a Fortune 500 company.









